name: Prima Trifia
description: As children we hunted together in the forests of Vieja Amazonia to impress our families. it was impossible not to see the connection between us. She stared at me with all her eyes. Everyone saw us as the hope that would put an end to the three clans of hybrids that formed the two family branches. After separating as teenagers 10 Earth years ago, we didn't see each other again until a week ago.  She glowed in her newfound maturity and I let myself be seduced into the encounter. Only now, on the verge of being devoured, do I realise that her interest in me was only nutritional.  Translated with www.DeepL.com/Translator (free version)
